  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Capacity Building</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">All 3 projects covered by the Capacity Building aim to strengthen national systems to ensure their sustainability.

Eye Health: The overall goal of the project is to consolidate the gains of the previous projects and improve access to eye health in underserved areas in the spirit of universal access to eye health.

Inclusive education: Children with disabilities, including children with visual impairments, are educated alongside their peers within a wider government education system.

Political participation:  To increase the political participation of women and men with disabilities by promoting representation and active involvement in the local development dynamics and in the elections.</narrative>
  </description>
